Subject: [PATCH] Input: touchscreen: add Himax HX83121A SPI driver

Import the current in-tree HX83121A touchscreen driver split into SPI core and EGoTouchRev-derived algorithm files.
---
 drivers/input/touchscreen/Kconfig             |   12 +
 drivers/input/touchscreen/Makefile            |    2 +
 .../touchscreen/himax_hx83121a_spi_algo.c     | 1134 +++++++++++++
 .../touchscreen/himax_hx83121a_spi_algo.h     |  191 +++
 .../touchscreen/himax_hx83121a_spi_core.c     | 1478 +++++++++++++++++
 5 files changed, 2817 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 drivers/input/touchscreen/himax_hx83121a_spi_algo.c
